sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Webhook as odh-model-controller<br/>Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Controller as odh-model-controller<br/>Controller Manager
    participant Route as OpenShift Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Client as External Client
    participant NGC as NVIDIA NGC API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as RHOAI Dashboard
    participant ServingAPI as model-serving-api<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over User,Route: Flow 1: InferenceService Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: POST InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: OIDC/Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validating/Mutating Webhook<br/>TLS (cluster-internal)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admit (validated + defaulted)
    K8sAPI-->>User: InferenceService created

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService events<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Note over Controller: Delta processing:<br/>compute desired state,<br/>compare with existing

    par Create supplementary resources
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ClusterRoleBinding<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Metrics Service<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create KEDA TriggerAuth<br/>TLS 1.2+, SA Token
    end

    Client->>Route: Inference Request<br/>HTTPS TLS (edge/re-encrypt)
    Route-->>Client: Prediction Response

    Note over Controller,NGC: Flow 2: NIM Account Reconciliation

    Controller->>K8sAPI: Watch NIM Account CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>NGC: POST /proxy_auth (nvcr.io)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: Runtime Token
    Controller->>NGC: GET /v2/org/models (api.ngc.nvidia.com)<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, API Key
    NGC-->>Controller: Model Catalog

    par Create NIM resources
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Pull Secret<br/>(dockerconfigjson)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update ConfigMap<br/>(model catalog)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Templates<br/>(NIM ServingRuntimes)
    end

    Note over Dashboard,ServingAPI: Flow 3: Gateway Discovery

    Dashboard->>ServingAPI: GET /api/v1/gateways?namespace=ns<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+ (FIPS ciphers)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (user token)
    ServingAPI->>K8sAPI: SelfSubjectAccessReview<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, User Token
    K8sAPI-->>ServingAPI: Allowed/Denied

    alt Authorized
        ServingAPI->>K8sAPI: List Gateways<br/>HTTPS TLS 1.2+, SA Token
        K8sAPI-->>ServingAPI: Gateway List
        ServingAPI-->>Dashboard: JSON Gateway Response
    else Unauthorized
        ServingAPI-->>Dashboard: 403 Forbidden
    end
